    public class AnnotateWeaklyConnectedComponents<G extends GraphHead,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge,LG extends BaseGraph<G,V,E,LG,GC>,GC extends BaseGraphCollection<G,V,E,LG,GC>>
extends GradoopGellyAlgorithm<G,V,E,LG,GC,GradoopId,org.apache.flink.types.NullValue>
    A gradoop operator wrapping Flinks ScatterGatherIteration-Algorithm for ConnectedComponents ConnectedComponents. The result will be the same BaseGraph with a component id assigned to each vertex as a property. If annotateEdges is set to true, the component id is assigned to each edge as a property, too.
